      <intermediateExchange id="17c0b602-8cfe-5260-a15c-bf20d7720773" unitId="487df68b-4994-4027-8fdc-a4dc298257b7" variableName="packaging_p" amount="0.000431806490066225" intermediateExchangeId="567c1e2d-b33a-4bf5-b4ad-d69926ce2f89" activityLinkId="f3da446d-c5d3-5187-bc6b-f07fc0f57771">
        <name xml:lang="en">packaging, for pesticides</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">Total amount of active substance/s of pesticides used for the production of sweet corn is calculated to be about 3.05 kg/ha (Kanissery et al 2022, IPM 2002, Clemson Extension 2020). The total amount of active substance/s is doubled in order to account for the packaging of the dilluted product of pesticides that are applied. Therefore,  6.09kg of packaging for pesticides per ha of Sweet Corn( 4.32E-4kg/kg) is calculated with this exchange.</comment>
